data.description: Step into this exceptional 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in West San Antonio, perfectly positioned near Lackland and Kelly AFB with convenient shopping and dining options nearby. Boasting striking curb appeal and a covered carport, this home welcomes you into a beautifully maintained interior that radiates modern charm and the latest updates. The spacious kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and ample room for culinary adventures. Enjoy the comfort of large bedrooms and a mostly carpet-free interior, enhancing the home's sleek appeal. Outside, a large backyard features a covered patio, ideal for outdoor entertaining or quiet relaxation. This home combines practicality with style, making it an outstanding choice for anyone looking to live near military bases while enjoying the comforts of contemporary living.
